# Faz 6: Task Management

## Goal

Task claim endpoint (`POST /tasks/:id/claim`) — pessimistic lock + peer eviction (competitive mode). Task complete endpoint (`POST /tasks/:id/complete`) — action-based (`APPROVE`, `REJECT`, `REQUEST_REVISION`, etc.) per workflow. Task form schema dynamic rendering (JSON schema → form). SLA badge + overdue tracking. Task list (my tasks + all tasks). Task detail screen.

## Bu fazın çalışma modeli (iterasyonlar)

`@56-phase-06-task-management` + **“Faz 6 — İterasyon N”**.

### İterasyon 1 — Tasks API + SLA + worker cron

**Hedef:** `tasks/*`, `task-sla.service`, claim/complete kuralları, overdue cron consumer; concurrency/race testleri; notification emit noktaları (stub veya gerçek event — Faz 7’ye bırakılacaksa doc’ta not).

**Minimum bağlam:** `docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` 9.7; `docs/02_DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` tasks.

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** RHF dinamik form UI (İter 2).

**Stop:** [ ] Integration race test; [ ] SLA cron testi. PR/onay.

### İterasyon 2 — Frontend task list/detail + dinamik form + E2E

**Hedef:** `S-TASK-LIST`, `S-MY-TASKS`, `S-TASK-DETAIL`, `TaskForm` (schema→RHF+Zod), SLA badge, kritik E2E (manager approves KTİ task).

**Stop:** Faz 6 Done Definition; roadmap işareti.

