apps/api/src/tasks/
├── tasks.module.ts
├── tasks.controller.ts
├── tasks.service.ts                      # claim, complete, cancel
├── tasks.exceptions.ts
├── task-sla.service.ts                   # SLA compute + overdue check
└── dto/*.ts

apps/api/src/worker/
└── src/tasks/sla-checker-cron.ts         # Overdue marking cron
```

### Frontend

```
apps/web/src/app/(app)/
├── tasks/page.tsx                         # S-TASK-LIST (all accessible)
├── my-tasks/page.tsx                      # S-MY-TASKS (assigned to me)
└── tasks/[id]/page.tsx                    # S-TASK-DETAIL

apps/web/src/components/tasks/
├── TaskList.tsx
├── TaskDetail.tsx
├── TaskForm.tsx                           # Dynamic from form_schema
├── TaskActions.tsx                        # Action buttons per allowed_actions
└── SlaBadge.tsx                           # From shared components
```

## Constraints

- Claim: `FOR UPDATE` lock, first-claim wins, peer task_assignees deleted
- Complete: only claimed_by_user_id matches actor
- Action validation: step.allowedActions içinde olmalı
- Reason required for REJECT, REQUEST_REVISION
- form_data validation: step.formSchema Zod şemasına karşı
- SLA due_at: task creation + step.slaMinutes
- Overdue cron: 5 dk'da bir taramalı, `is_overdue` flag update
- Notification emit on: task created, task claimed, task completed, SLA approaching, SLA overdue

