## Explicit Don'ts

- Task comments (post-MVP)
- Task subtasks (sub-process — post-MVP)
- Task delegation (different from assignment — post-MVP)
- Task priority levels (all tasks equal in MVP)
- Task escalation automation (manager escalation post-MVP)

## Related ADRs

